title: Workflow
text:
This page describes my workflow.


Data can be found on the MLIT Dataset : https://www.reinfolib.mlit.go.jp/realEstatePrices/. It contains all the real estates price transactions all over Japan since 2003.

# Load libraries
library(ggplot2)




Perform your analysis here.

# Example plot
ggplot(mtcars, aes(x = wt, y = mpg)) +
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(title = "Car Weight vs MPG")












library(ggplot2)

Document your findings and conclusions.
